Assumptions:

* Products information will be supplied via a valid JSON file (Sample: products.json)
* Prices are positive float numbers.
* Currency is Euros by default
* Stock management or product availability check isn't part of the scope
* Pricing Rules input(OPTIONAL) is supplied in either of the specified format
  'CODE': { min: x, discount: x }
  'CODE': { every: 2, discount: x }
* Maximum of One pricing rule per product
* Discount can be fixed(0 to price) or percentage(0 to 100)
